songs.title: Change Your Life
songs.lyrics:
[Intro: Lil Mosey]
Aye Royce, you did it right here

[Verse 1: Lil Mosey]
Countin' these bands in my brand new whip
Boy you look cool, with this ice like a pimp
Everyone start talkin', when you are receiving them checks
They say lil bro', they watch how you live
They say Lil Mosey, you ain't talkin' like this
I just hit the wraith, with a brand new bitch
Cartier glasses, on some rockstar shit
Cartier glasses, on some rockstar shit

[Chorus: Sauve]
Ugh-agh, Why you wanna waste my time?
No, I, I wanna change your life, yeah
You're my dime, baby come spend the night
Just touch the sky, cause i wanna change your life, yeah

[Verse 2: Lil Mosey]
We can go out to the moon
We can catch up, I'll just buy you some shoes
Sometimes i felt that we wasn't too cool
My diamonds seein' you walk in my room
We at your neck, to buy my bitch a purse
She tryna impress, she screamin' okurr
Pourin' the wok, you know I'm finna burst
They say we up, but we need money first

[Chorus: Sauve]
Ugh-agh, Why you wanna waste my time?
No, I, I wanna change your life, yeah
You're my dime, baby come spend the night
Just touch the sky, cause i wanna change your life, yeah

[Verse 3: Sauve]
We robbin' shops, bitch we spend it like Tiffany
I gave you my heart, so I know that you feelin' me
We rockin' gold chains, so bitch give me sympathy
I'm gettin' checks, now they treatin' me generally
(?)
Fuck with the gang, no matter you dead
She said she proud of me chasin' baguettes
Give her the racks, then give her a visa

[Chorus: Sauve]
Ugh-agh, Why you wanna waste my time?
No, I, I wanna change your life, yeah
You're my dime, baby come spend the night
Just touch the sky, cause i wanna change your life, yeah
